  "title": "QS Consultant - Training Provided!!!  | 1618",
  "description": "<p><strong>Quantity Surveyor</strong></p><p>Working Hours: Mon to Fri, 9am - 6pm</p><p>Salary: 3,000 - 4.200</p><p>Location:Bukit Merah Central</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Recognised Degree/Diploma in Quantity Surveying/Building or equivalent qualifications</li><li>2 to 5 years of relevant working experience in a consultancy firm preferred</li><li>Proficient in QS application and software</li><li>Training Provided for entry level</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Involvement in the overall quantity surveying, cost & contract management of projects</li><li>Feasibility studies & early cost advice.</li><li>Preparation of cost estimate & cost plan</li><li>Value management & cost management</li><li>Advice and management of the overall procurement process</li><li>Preparation of tender & contract documentation</li><li>Evaluation of tenders received, analysis & reporting</li><li>Measurement and taking-off of quantities and quantification of works done</li><li>Valuation of progress payment claim, variation and final account</li><li>Attendance to project & site meeting</li></ul><p><br />Chin Wai Loon Reg No: R24121618</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
